<br>
I have also bought software for others or given them software I obtained for free (i.e. GenCon, Fan Faire, other promotional).<br>
<br>
I really don't want it trivial to have a 2nd or 3rd character.  THAT encourages the griefing because one can quickly switch from one character to another on the same account.  Yes, someone can have more than one account, but it is not as likely.<br>
<br>
This is about the only place where I do approve of RL money making a difference in EQ. <p>&lt;center&gt;<br>
